io.sphere.sdk.shoppinglists

Interface TextLineItem


  • public interface TextLineItem
    A TextLineItem has a name, a description and a quantity. A TextLineItem can have custom fields.
    See Also:
    AddTextLineItem, RemoveTextLineItem, ChangeTextLineItemQuantity, ChangeTextLineItemName, SetTextLineItemDescription, SetTextLineItemCustomField, * @see ShoppingList#getTextLineItems()
